List of Mapped Countries for DAM Prices

Source: R/entsoe_countries.R
entsoe_countries.Rd

This data table contains a mapping of countries to their respective EIC codes for retrieving DAM prices from the ENTSOE Transparency Platform API.

Usage

entsoe_countries

Format

An object of class data.table (inherits from data.frame) with 43 rows and 5 columns.

Examples

library(entsoeapi)
#> Error in library(entsoeapi): there is no package called 'entsoeapi'
entsoe_countries
